column2: "People back then didn't know much, but they undestood everything. Today we know a lot, but don't understand anything."
"Paska on talonpojan kultaa - Shit is a peasant's gold."
"Mikä laulaen tulee, se viheltäen menee." - "What comes singing, will leave whistling."
"Joutsen on ihmisestä rikottu linnuksi" - "A swan has been broken from man into a bird."
